{"tid":800408,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"被美少女耽誤的漫畫家　冨樫義博現身欅坂46夏季巡演","createTime":"2018-08-31T00:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T06:05:11.000Z","uid":38049,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dfaabaaf5ee06a546f7c3595f82eda6325a233bc","tid":800408,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:14:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180829/1246762.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180829%2F1246762.htm&d=YaD4eHlGJtkOGsmHzZwWNfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=9e7f500a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180829/1246762.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/081323_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F081323_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bbea7161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n被美少女耽誤的漫畫家　冨樫義博現身欅坂46夏季巡演<br />\n <br />\n日本漫畫《獵人》從連載以來經常性休刊，作者冨樫義博也被網友戲稱是「富奸」。關於他的休刊原因更是眾說紛紜，像是玩電動、腰痛無法行走等各式各樣的猜測，而近期則是迷上了日本女子團體，甚至像個小粉絲一樣，現身她們的夏季巡演。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/080517_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F080517_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f65cbc2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲獵人作者現身欅坂46夏季巡演。（圖／翻攝自バグベアのこぎみいい推特）<br />\n<br />\n▲獵人作者冨樫義博（中）現身欅坂46夏季巡演。（圖／翻攝自バグベアのこぎみいい推特）<br />\n<br />\n冨樫這次迷上的女團是「櫸坂46」，目前有41名成員，並且分成「漢字組（櫸坂 46）」以及「平假名組（けやき坂 46）」。原先平假名組的成員是櫸坂46的二軍成員，但後來也因為2017年獨立演出電視劇後擁有不少支持者，所以越來越有獨立成團的趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/080543_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F080543_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=026a8f67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲每次欅坂46演出，冨樫的花籃總是會出現。<br />\n<br />\n而今年年初けやき坂 46在日本武道館公演上，冨樫義博也送了祝賀花籃到現場。知名歌曲的作曲編曲組合バグベア （Bugbear）更在推特上放上了一張照片，是他們與冨樫在欅坂46夏季巡演Live上，一同比出欅坂46招牌動作的合照，讓許多網友對獵人的復刊瞬間又充滿了信心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w6ABMtg_nsU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw6ABMtg_nsU&d=YaD4eHlGJtkOGsmHzZwWNfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=a5d9a31d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w6ABMtg_nsU</a><br />\n<br />\n▲▼不但念能力撞名歌曲，連念人偶都神似成員平手友梨奈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/080658_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F080658_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=0aa18efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除了親自參加欅坂46活動，從2017年開始《獵人》中也出現許多與她們相關的情節。像是角色修利科夫的念能力日文翻譯是「沉默的多數」，也就是櫸坂46的成名歌曲，而身邊的人偶也神似團中成員平手友梨奈，以及角色擺出けやき坂 46招牌動作等。甚至冨樫義博還透過漫畫角色，來解釋自己到底是喜愛漢字組的櫸坂 46，還是平假名組的けやき坂 46，證明他自己真的是去「取材」才休刊的。<br />\n<br />\n▼連角色都擺出欅坂46招牌動作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/081146_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F081146_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bb1154d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n ▼「漢字欅跟平假名欅，你喜歡哪一個呢？」 「這是世界上最愚蠢的問題之一，我沒辦法選擇」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/080733_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F080733_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=58303903&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19b0e5ced8f140fb90325f9cc4558f41e5b43682","tid":800408,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:15:14.000Z","msg":"你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace4cf23bb8721eccbe9e88aa3da274ec132851c","tid":800408,"uid":19012,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:19:54.000Z","msg":"佢屋企隻乸未就係美少女始祖囉<br />\n<br />\n駛鬼出街搵咩"},{"pid":"b919628eb706fe64ac0c95edbe06ee2b9fa3fd23","tid":800408,"uid":61210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:20:54.000Z","msg":"講咁耐即係幾時再連載？"},{"pid":"3185c866e87314ac1fcded82a7536da8d33e7806","tid":800408,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:05:11.000Z","msg":"去實地取材啫,下話"}]}